[su_note note_color="#ecece6" radius="9"]

Car Dealer Theme

[su_animate] CarDealer Free WordPress (theme) is the easiest way to manage, list and sell your cars and vehicles online. With OnLine guide, support and demo. Really built for Car Dealer business not for Car Classified Websites. You can also use this theme with our plugin Multidealer (Multi Dealer Plugin) instead of Car Dealer Plugin. We have incorporated many theme options which significantly reducing the time required to setup your website. Features
